Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:07.99,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the Ancient Dragon is \Napproaching much faster than anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:11.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But the Queen's fleet \Nshould be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.99,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it's taking longer \Nto get additional cannons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:20.09,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:21.70,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen leagues, south-southeast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.93,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the fleet \Nwon't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:03.00,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Zero's Familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:21.77,OnScreen,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.82,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Gandalfr rune...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.01,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My contract with Louise is still active.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:40.30,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I forced Louise to make \Nsuch a sad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone who can't even make \Nthe girl he loves smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}isn't a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.44,CRZero,Reynald,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:00.30,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.08,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.77,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,It's a counter from the \Naboriginal school of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.09,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,They use tools to fortify \Nthe power of the spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:52.09,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these Elemental \NSiblings, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.91,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,You see, never a boring day in \Nthe land of the barbarians.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:59.97,CRZero,Damien,0000,0000,0000,,Since the area is so big, \Nit might not last too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.12,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,For now it's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:05.72,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope this lasts \Nuntil the fleet arrives...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.39,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.26,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a flight of dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.57,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to get back to Halkeginia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.04,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:19.27,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's got to be a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.46,CRZero,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.83,CRZero,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to buy that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.23,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:39.99,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.22,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I can't buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.30,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.87,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't break from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.48,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.11,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,The fleet is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.65,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,To all ships of the Halkeginia Alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:30.01,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Ready the cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.67,CRZero,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Load the shells!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:36.21,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.80,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to thank you for your \Ncooperation, Miss Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:47.19,CRZero,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strange day, \Nfor me to fight alongside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:53.17,CRZero,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Not for our personal past, \Nbut for the entire world's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:56.30,CRZero,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it everything \Nwe've got, Mr. Colbert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.72,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:04.42,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,If this attack succeeds, the magic \Nbarrier should be dispelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:08.61,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if Louise then casts her \NExplosion, it will surely work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.48,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.27,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.82,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Round two, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.17,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.30,CRZero,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.05,CRZero,Knight2,0000,0000,0000,,It's a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.92,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:03.77,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.66,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Bidalsha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.55,CRZero,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,The elves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.85,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,By combining the power of the \Nspirits with this fire stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.89,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,we can create a fire barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.36,CRZero,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea it could be used that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.19,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps Joseph's rampage was
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.22,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,actually brought on by a greater power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.98,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Nephthys fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:35.23,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Bidalsha came, \Njust like he promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:37.61,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew there were this many elves
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:39.14,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,who support friendship with the barbarians!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.31,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.06,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.45,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Ask my brother Damien!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.67,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.77,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,F-Flan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.77,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.18,CRZero,Damien,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this is no longer of use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.32,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.99,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Fireball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.62,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:40.94,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:43.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon is after you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:44.94,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.64,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Illococoo, can you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.14,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.06,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.45,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:37.23,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Midois Algiz Delcana Manlagun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.18,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.10,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.85,CRZero,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,My lady, shall we fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:53.50,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:57.14,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,If you attack now, you might \Nhit Louise and Tiffania.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.68,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The magic barrier was torn \Nopen by the previous attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.01,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Aoren Suhn Fil Yarnsaksa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:16.42,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Osu Suhn Uryn Rurin Lagon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:17.36,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Windy Icicle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.73,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Deoru Yuru Sugia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.39,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Fly, my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:24.97,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ossia Jer Undil...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.31,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.74,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Hagal Beocs Fil...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.82,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.23,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.18,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,My strength is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.08,OnScreen,Headline,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(209,1)}A Total Eclipse Over Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,They said that flying into
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:46.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,an eclipse might bring \Nme back to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:47.95,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, then the \Nopposite must be true as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.82,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.51,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:24.09,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.59,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.79,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Did Saito actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.29,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Saito came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:01.29,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.23,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's Halkeginia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:06.09,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,This is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:09.00,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that'd actually work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.19,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Derf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:16.21,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Have you been well, pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.89,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Have I been well? Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:24.29,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I'm not \Nquite sure I understand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:29.17,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I was sleeping in \Nyour rune after the sword broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.04,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You were sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.69,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.06,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive, that's all that counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:37.34,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:40.73,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.50,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.43,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, the magic barrier is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:13.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.21,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.16,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Great timing, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:29.69,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:31.40,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:34.47,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It took me so long to \Nfinally make up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.47,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:35.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:36.59,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.82,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect this world, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:45.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So let's take him down, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:50.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to attack him again and \Nget rid of his magic barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:53.89,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Then you cast your Explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.67,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm all out of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:14:59.41,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.33,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.52,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If you use your Lífþrasir \Npower, your life is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:06.08,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:06.75,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.14,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:14.71,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If you die then... \NI have no reason to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.50,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, I promise you, \NI'm not going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.21,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd leave behind \Nthe person I love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I am your...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:30.95,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I am Zero's familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:33.67,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:46.03,OnScreen,Song,0000,0000,0000,,First kiss kara hajimaru  futari no koi no hisutori\NOur love's history starts with the first kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:54.58,OnScreen,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei ni mahou kaketa  kimi ga totsuzen arawareta\NI cast a spell on this fate  then you suddenly appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:01.91,OnScreen,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuki ga futatsu kienai sora\NThe sky where the two moons never disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:03.25,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can feel Saito's life force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:07.93,OnScreen,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Arienai koto da yo ne\NThis is unbelievable
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.66,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do it!
